parameters:
Photography Club President: President Memimi, can I have a
moment? Hehehe...

Memimi: (It's the president of the Photography Club... He
poured all his part-time job earnings into his camera, and
it's a really good one... And now, he's using that camera to
take a full-on shot of my lower half...)

Photography Club President: I bought this camera, so I can
use it now, right? I sold my old camera and somehow managed
to get enough money... I'll take pictures of us having sex,
sell them, and buy a new camera... hehehe...

Memimi: (...This is a nightmare... It has to be a dream...
To think that even a male student would do something like
this to me... Aaaaah...!)
